{"tid":220174,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知鴨寮街邊檔有賣呢樣嘢？","createTime":"2017-04-27T18:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T18:10:05.000Z","uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1516898c930beb0c6f1e9fa38f89f71f2f95cf","tid":220174,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:32:25.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個sound detector module<br />\n畀5V電，個MIC會收音，然後輸出\b音量值（AO）同埋HIGH／LOW（DO）<br />\n想知鴨寮街邊檔有賣，最緊要有Analog output，即係四腳<br />\n最好有多幾款可以畀我買哂嚟試<br />\n<br />\n之前喺淘寶買咗呢款，靈敏度極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要對正個MIC發聲個輸出值先少少有\b變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BKPUCau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBKPUCau.jpg&h=8600c0a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就睇過YOUTUBE效果唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZKR5Lhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZKR5Lhb.jpg&h=44d23fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8096c828e6df78223fc91ed09617dee391d21c10","tid":220174,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:16:24.000Z","msg":"Diy友去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1200e27adb2186f148397753fe68d417c9837678","tid":220174,"uid":109694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"上Sparkfun搵下 有保證"},{"pid":"b34e937f79f33f2f55a2e7eba06f3817f28f9600","tid":220174,"uid":27980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:27:57.000Z","msg":"上華輝搵"},{"pid":"8b88823e9cee21bd5752bc5a8a313eede3565f1d","tid":220174,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T20:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上華輝搵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854a6e8ead769824211d0f4173895c3ebda2e0b9","tid":220174,"uid":23094,"